## 7 ┬Ę Usecase 2 ŌĆö Discover & Convert

1. `bridge_list_layers` ŌåÆ identify component candidates
2. `bridge_create_component` ŌåÆ convert eligible nodes (FRAME, GROUP ŌĆö not TEXT)
3. `bridge_save_component_spec` ŌåÆ save spec for each
4. `bridge_save_connections` ŌåÆ save mappings

Ō£ģ **Done only when the completion gate (section 3) is satisfied.**

